# Cyber Risk Classifier — Environment Variables
# 
# To enable the AI Threat Report feature:
# 1. Get a free API key from https://console.anthropic.com
# 2. Copy this file and rename it to .env
# 3. Replace the value below with your actual key
# 4. Run: export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY="your-actual-key-here"

ANTHROPIC_API_KEY="your-anthropic-api-key-here"
